The '''1995 [[South Asian Games]]''' (or '''7th SAF Games''') were held in [[Madras]], [[India]] between 18 and 27 December 1995.<ref>National Sports Council, Nepal [http://nsc.gov.np/South%20Asian%20Games-Total%20Medal%20tally.pdf "South Asian Games"]. Retrieved on 16 February 2011</ref>

